g.text: United Kingdom released an estimated 381 MtCO2e in 2023 (excl. LULUCF), a change of -6.7 % compared to the previous year.
Per capita GHG emissions were 5.6 tCO2e in 2023. Cumulative CO2 emissions since 1850 were 78.2 GtCO2, or about 3% of global
emissions to date. Sources: EDGAR v9, GCB 2023, UNFCCC, Grassi et al. 2021
